# Environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env` for local development:
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# The base template has no required variables. As you add features that import
# from `$env/static/*`, document every key here with a placeholder value (never
# an empty string) so that `pnpm build` and CI can resolve them. After adding or
# changing keys, run `pnpm sync` to regenerate the SvelteKit env types.
#
# Example (uncomment and adapt when you add a database):
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/app
